snippet: Spencer Levin holed out from a greenside bunker for eagle on the par-4 17th and shot an eight-under 63 to take a three-stroke lead in the suspended second round of the Phoenix Open in Scottsdale, Ariz.
abstract: Spencer Levin takes three-stroke lead in suspended second round at the Phoenix Open golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: Spencer Levin holed out from a greenside bunker for eagle on the par-4 17th and shot an eight-under 63 to take a three-stroke lead in the suspended second round of the Phoenix Open in Scottsdale, Ariz.
